{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2017/07/19/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Azure - 在 Azure 上使用 Azure Container Service 來執行 Kubernetes","date":"19 July 2017","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Azure","Container","ACS","Kubernetes","Docker","Linux"],"coverImage":null},"id":"e2de8e5c-9c9e-5613-95ad-6eecf137569c","html":"<h2>警告</h2>\n<p>Azure Container Service 已經成 Azure Kubernetes Service，這篇已經棄用</p>\n<p>新文章請參考<a href=\"http://skychang.github.io/2020/03/21/Azure-Create_Azure_Kubernetes_Service/\">這篇</a></p>\n<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>Azure Container Service 一直是小弟想找時間好好玩的一個 Azure 服務，從今年年初提到的 DC/OS ，到上個月分享的 Kubernetes，老實說，都是個非常好玩，且強大的服務，但今年 ( 其實從去年 ) 就一直忙碌到現在，所以也變成沒有充裕的時間可以好好的來寫一下這方面的文章：而在這次又因為要上課，所以想說，就在把安裝過程記錄一下，不然老實說，這個過程還滿多眉眉角角的：舉例來說，一開始，可能要先去 AD 註冊應用程式 ( Kubernetes 要求.. )，為了安全性，可能只會提供這個 Resource Group 的使用權，然後要設定 SSH Key ，最後才能進入服務的啟用...</p>\n<p>所以，其實還滿多東西要處理的，好吧，廢話不多說，就此開始吧！</p>\n<h2>使用 AZ 快速設定</h2>\n<p>在開始前，如果您真的不想用 UI 操作，那一堆設定，<a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-kubernetes-service-principal\">官方網站</a>也提供了快速建立初期步驟的一些流程：而小弟這篇，則會使用 UI 的操作方式來建立。</p>\n<h2>設定 Resource Group</h2>\n<p>首先，我們要先建立一個空的 Resource Group：雖然，我們可以在建立 ACS ( Azure Container Service ) 的過程中，順便建立 Resource Group，但我們這邊為了讓流程順一點，我們就先來建立一個空的 Resource Group 吧。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/89066/01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"01\"\n        title=\"01\"\n        src=\"/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/78d47/01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/56d15/01.png 200w,\n/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/d9f49/01.png 400w,\n/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/78d47/01.png 800w,\n/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/64756/01.png 1200w,\n/static/3fb106cc6184a57a80b12c561d4533a9/89066/01.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>這樣就完成第一步驟。</p>\n<h2>設定 AD 應用程式註冊</h2>\n<p>完成第一步驟後，我們接下來要設定 AD 的 應用程式註冊，在使用 ACS Kubetnetes 之前，Kubetnetes 需要我們提供 AD 應用程式註冊的相關資訊，所以我們必須先完成此事。</p>\n<p>首先，我們需要新增一個新的應用程式註冊。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/89066/02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"02\"\n        title=\"02\"\n        src=\"/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/78d47/02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/56d15/02.png 200w,\n/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/d9f49/02.png 400w,\n/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/78d47/02.png 800w,\n/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/64756/02.png 1200w,\n/static/2aa9c87567a081619919aac48dd72690/89066/02.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>這邊填入相關資訊，其中在這邊，登入 URL 只是一個識別，可以隨意填，不用真的是一個網址。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/89066/03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"03\"\n        title=\"03\"\n        src=\"/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/78d47/03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/56d15/03.png 200w,\n/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/d9f49/03.png 400w,\n/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/78d47/03.png 800w,\n/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/64756/03.png 1200w,\n/static/aba985c18cf59fe1edc9310f9a83bbe9/89066/03.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>新增完成後，我們可以進行一些微調 ( 這邊微調的用意，只是希望能和官方的 Script 產生出來的結果一樣 )\n基本上，我們用不到回覆 URL 所以可以直接砍掉。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/89066/04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"04\"\n        title=\"04\"\n        src=\"/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/78d47/04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/56d15/04.png 200w,\n/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/d9f49/04.png 400w,\n/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/78d47/04.png 800w,\n/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/64756/04.png 1200w,\n/static/d50235e9f799161112c701538c5ac6fd/89066/04.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，我們要產生此帳號的金鑰，名稱和有效期限可以隨意，按下儲存後，就會產生出金鑰，這個金鑰到時候會需要用在 ACS 的建立中，所以請複製下來：如果沒複製下來，離開此頁後，就再也看不到了 XDD\n( 當然，可以砍掉重新建立一個也是可以低~ )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/89066/05.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"05\"\n        title=\"05\"\n        src=\"/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/78d47/05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/56d15/05.png 200w,\n/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/d9f49/05.png 400w,\n/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/78d47/05.png 800w,\n/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/64756/05.png 1200w,\n/static/4e0836973cf114e4e8380f55dcbe0e98/89066/05.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>最後，回到屬性頁，我們可以調整一下應用程式識別碼 URI，雖然不調整也是可以，但調整一下，未來會比較清楚這是拿來做啥的。\n另外，特別重要的地方是黃色框框的應用程式識別碼，這個也請複製下來，雖然不回不見，但等下建立 ACS 的時候，會比較方便。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/89066/06.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"06\"\n        title=\"06\"\n        src=\"/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/78d47/06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/56d15/06.png 200w,\n/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/d9f49/06.png 400w,\n/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/78d47/06.png 800w,\n/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/64756/06.png 1200w,\n/static/ed9f090d448c36890eb6268e00619847/89066/06.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，回到資源群組 Resource Group，我們要把剛剛建立的帳號，授權可使用此資源群組ㄌ。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/89066/07.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"07\"\n        title=\"07\"\n        src=\"/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/78d47/07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/56d15/07.png 200w,\n/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/d9f49/07.png 400w,\n/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/78d47/07.png 800w,\n/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/64756/07.png 1200w,\n/static/c933c9b8052176ee1e18b3ee26b51e2a/89066/07.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>完成如下。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/89066/08.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"08\"\n        title=\"08\"\n        src=\"/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/78d47/08.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/56d15/08.png 200w,\n/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/d9f49/08.png 400w,\n/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/78d47/08.png 800w,\n/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/64756/08.png 1200w,\n/static/7d31ea383a8a764cc8346b995f08cec3/89066/08.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>到此，就完成了 AD 應用程式註冊應用程式註冊的部分。</p>\n<h2>建立 ACS Kubernetes</h2>\n<p>接著，我們就要開始建立 ACS 了，如下圖，我們可以從這邊新增</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/89066/09.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"09\"\n        title=\"09\"\n        src=\"/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/78d47/09.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/56d15/09.png 200w,\n/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/d9f49/09.png 400w,\n/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/78d47/09.png 800w,\n/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/64756/09.png 1200w,\n/static/73f7e08988f8ac9ba479ae79e0499569/89066/09.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>首先，第一頁的選項，如下，記得資源群組要選擇剛剛建立的。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/89066/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/78d47/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/56d15/10.png 200w,\n/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/d9f49/10.png 400w,\n/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/78d47/10.png 800w,\n/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/64756/10.png 1200w,\n/static/40f268e2088a4f811fb7efc8d75266f3/89066/10.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，Orchestrator 我們選擇 Kubernetes，當然，ACS 不只支援 Kubernetes，也支援 DC/OS 等，但小弟這邊與未來的文章，目前基本上是專注於 Kubernetes ( DC/OS 表示 ... )，所以小弟我這邊就選擇 Kubernetes。</p>\n<p>Dns name prefix 表示網址的前置詞，這邊就使用 study4，未來就會以 study4 為開頭的網址。</p>\n<p>接下來要輸入 User Name 和 SSH Public Key。\n如果沒有 SSH Public Key 的朋友，可以<a href=\"https://skychang.github.io/2015/10/19/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/\">參考這篇</a>，裡面的中間，有提到做法可以產生 Key。( 上面有不同平台可以選擇 )</p>\n<p>而 Public Key 的預設位置在 ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub\nMac 和 Linux 就是家目錄的隱藏資料夾。\n如果是 Windows 就是帳號目錄底下隱藏資料夾。</p>\n<p>我們只需要把 id_rsa.pub 打開，並且貼到 Azure Portal 即可。</p>\n<p>接下來，就是把剛剛我們黃色框框的內容，貼到 Service principal clientID。\n把剛剛在 AD 應用程式註冊產生的金鑰貼到 Service Principal client secret。</p>\n<p>最後，可以選擇要開幾台 Master，如果怕掛，就多開幾台，但就是要多收幾倍的錢 XDDD</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/89066/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11\"\n        title=\"11\"\n        src=\"/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/78d47/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/56d15/11.png 200w,\n/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/d9f49/11.png 400w,\n/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/78d47/11.png 800w,\n/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/64756/11.png 1200w,\n/static/620a5b33092b18b3013ffe2552489655/89066/11.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>到下一頁後，我們可以選擇要幾台 Agent，和 Master 不同，Master 是控管整個 Kubernetes 環境的機器，而 Agent 則是提供放置 Docker ( 我們開發的應用程式的環境 )。</p>\n<p>然後可以選擇要哪種規模的 Agent。</p>\n<p>最後，再選擇是要 Windows 還是 Linux，當然，這就會牽扯到，Docker 是要運行在 Windows 上，還是 Linux 上。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/89066/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"12\"\n        title=\"12\"\n        src=\"/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/78d47/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/56d15/12.png 200w,\n/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/d9f49/12.png 400w,\n/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/78d47/12.png 800w,\n/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/64756/12.png 1200w,\n/static/92e31bd53b7324316a161414012f7c1f/89066/12.png 1440w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>完成後，按下確認，就可以開始進行部署了。</p>\n<p>下篇，會開始討論，如何操作與控制 ACS Kubernetes。</p>\n<h2>後記</h2>\n<p>雖然整篇的建置看起來很簡單，但在第一次建置的時候，其實還遇到滿多麻煩的，再加上官方文章其實也是跳來跳去，所以小弟就在這邊整理了一下整個流程，希望對大家有幫助嚕!..</p>\n<p>P.S ACS 的服務不便宜，所以請作量使用....</p>\n<h2>參考資料</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-kubernetes-service-principal\">https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-kubernetes-service-principal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-deployment\">https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-deployment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/ad/sp\">https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/cli/azure/ad/sp</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-kubernetes-walkthrough\">https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/azure/container-service/container-service-kubernetes-walkthrough</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://skychang.github.io/2015/10/19/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/\">https://skychang.github.io/2015/10/19/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"警告 Azure Container Service 已經成 Azure Kubernetes Service，這篇已經棄用 新文章請參考這篇 前言 Azure Container Service 一直是小弟想找時間好好玩的一個 Azure 服務，從今年年初提到的 DC/OS…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Redis - 在 Windows 上建立高可用性的 Redis","tags":["Redis","Windows"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2017/04/09/Redis-Create_Redis_HA/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Redis-Create_Redis_HA/Redis-Create_Redis_HA.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Azure - Azure Container Service - Kubernetes 第一次的部署","tags":["Azure","Container","ACS","Kubernetes","Docker","Linux"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2017/07/30/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create/Azure-Azure_Container_Service_Kubernetes_First_Create.md"}}}}